{
  "name": "Medical Release Expert",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-blue.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Ninjutsu </p><p>Prerequisite: Level 8+, Medical Keyword </p><p>Every spark of life energy, corrupted dark chakra, or poisonous surge you manifest has a small piece of yourself within them.</p><p> You can command the powers of life and death.</p><p> When casting a Ninjutsu with the medical keyword, you gain the following benefits: </p><p>  - Increase your Intelligence or Wisdom score by 1, to a maximum of 20 </p><p>  - Acid, Poison or Necrotic damage you deal ignores resistance.</p><p>  - When you would restore creatures hit points, other than yourself, you gain a number of Temporary hit points equal to the number of healing dice rolled.</p><p>  - A jutsu cannot benefit from more than one \"X\" Release Expert feat at a time.</p>",
